                           page of <ref target="#ms_i1"/>, initial two lines of <ref target="#ms_i2"
                           />; initial words of all other texts and of each stanza; holy names (each
                           character alternates with black ink in the name of God on <locus
                              target="#21r"/>); names of the individuals related to the production
                           and ownership of the manuscript; partly elements of the punctuation
                           marks, text dividers, and numerals.</seg>
